={
  "sender": {
    "name": "JobRaahi Team",
    "email": "YOUR_SENDER_EMAIL@example.com"
  },
  "to": [
    {
      "email": "{{ $('Loop Over Colleges').item.json['Coordinator Email'] }}",
      "name": "{{ $('Loop Over Colleges').item.json['Coordinator Name'] }}"
    }
  ],
  "subject": "Thank You for Connecting with Job Raahi — Next Steps Enclosed",
  "htmlContent": "<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p><p>Hope you are doing well.</p><p>It was great speaking with you today! I am Gargi from Job Raahi — a free digital job portal specifically designed for ITI, Polytechnic, and entry-level candidates across India.</p><p>As discussed on the call, Job Raahi helps students from institutions like yours directly connect with verified employers — at no cost whatsoever.</p><p><strong>What students get on Job Raahi:</strong><br>• Registration is completely free<br>• Job applications are free — aaj bhi, kal bhi, aur future mein bhi<br>• Direct interview opportunities from verified employers across India<br>• City-wise, trade-wise, and skill-set-based job search<br>• Regular WhatsApp job alerts for new openings</p><p>Currently, the platform has <strong>3,000+ active job openings</strong> across manufacturing, automotive, electrical, aerospace, operations, and technical sectors — with new vacancies added regularly.</p><p>We work with reputed employers such as <strong>Amazon, JK Tyre, MG Motor, Ecozen Solutions, myTVS, Amber Group, Agile Robots, Indraprastha Gas Limited, and WSP</strong>, among others.</p><p><strong>How students can get started:</strong><br>• Download the Job Raahi app<br>• Complete registration and create their profile<br>• Apply directly to suitable job openings<br>• If profile matches, employer contacts them for interview</p><p>You are welcome to share this information with your faculty, admin team, or directly with students.</p><p><strong>Platform Link:</strong> <a href='https://www.YOUR_SENDER.com/'>https://www.YOUR_SENDER.com/</a></p><p>Looking forward to supporting your students with the right opportunities. Please feel free to connect anytime.</p><p>Thank you<br>Gargi – BDE<br>Job Raahi</p>"
}

={
  "sender": {
    "name": "JobRaahi Team",
    "email": "YOUR_SENDER_EMAIL@example.com"
