      "email": "{{ $('Loop Over Colleges').item.json['Coordinator Email'] }}",
      "name": "{{ $('Loop Over Colleges').item.json['Coordinator Name'] }}"
    }
  ],
  "subject": "Thank You from Job Raahi — Here for You Whenever the Need Arises",
  "htmlContent": "<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p><p>Thank you for taking the time to speak with us today.</p><p>I completely understand that there may not be an immediate requirement at your end right now — and that is perfectly fine.</p><p>I am Gargi from Job Raahi — a free digital job portal designed for ITI, Polytechnic, and entry-level candidates. The platform connects students directly with verified employers across India at absolutely no charge — no placement fees today, and no fees in the future either.</p><p><strong>At a glance — what Job Raahi offers:</strong><br>• 3,000+ active job openings across manufacturing, automotive, electrical, aerospace, and operations<br>• City-wise, trade-wise, and skill-set-based job search for students<br>• Direct employer connect — no middlemen, no charges<br>• Regular WhatsApp job alerts</p><p>Whenever your students are exploring opportunities in the future, Job Raahi will be there as a platform they can rely on — free of cost, always.</p><p><strong>Platform Link:</strong> <a href='https://www.YOUR_SENDER.com/'>https://www.YOUR_SENDER.com/</a></p><p>We would be happy to collaborate whenever suitable. Wishing you and your institution all the best!</p><p>Thank you<br>Gargi – BDE<br>Job Raahi</p>"
}

={
  "sender": {
    "name": "JobRaahi Team",
    "email": "YOUR_SENDER_EMAIL@example.com"
